

=Resources=

Via Dante Monson:

"Does anyone know of any standard or spec covering the formatting and structure of transcripts of sessions of Parliament? "

answers given :

* http://www.theyworkforyou.com/ (UK Parliament transcripts site) has a
** page introducing their parser: http://parser.theyworkforyou.com/ 
** page giving example XML from Hansard

Their software converts Government supplied Hansard data into a number of formats.

* This is used throughout the world in other Parliaments

